title: Futures edge lower ahead of weekly jobless claims, GDP numbers - Reuters
description: U.S. stock index futures edged lower on Thursday, a day after the S&P 500 and the Nasdaq hit record closing highs, as investors refrained from making big bets ahead of a barrage of economic data releases and the Federal Reserve's policy summit.
